      "content": "a break isn't really what i mean. i don't think a vacation or a few days off is gonna fix this. it's not just a bad week, it's like the foundation of my whole life is just... gone. everything i worked for is dead. it's just this constant, heavy ringing in my ears of how much i've wasted. i'm just so incredibly tired of fighting to exist in a world where i have nothing left to offer.",
