    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've called them. they just repeat the same scripts, the same \"it gets better\" lines. but it doesn't feel like it gets better, it just feels like the debt keeps growing. the debt of time, the debt of expectation. it feels like i'm just running on a treadmill that's getting faster and faster and i'm about to fall off. i just want to find some way to finally be still. to just have some actual peace where nothing is expected of me anymore.",
